2:T71f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Scalenut better than ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Scalenut scores 7.0 overall while ShortlyAI scores 5.0. Scalenut is best for SEO articles and content clusters, while ShortlyAI excels for blog posts and long-form articles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Scalenut or ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Scalenut starts at $39/mo and ShortlyAI starts at $79/mo. Scalenut offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Scalenut to ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Scalenut and ShortlyAI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Scalenut vs ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Scalenut holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. ShortlyAI has an overall rating of 5/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Scalenut for end-to-end seo content workflow in one tool and ShortlyAI for clean distraction-free interface."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Scalenut or ShortlyAI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Scalenut for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, ShortlyAI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize clean distraction-free interface. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","