10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Scalenut is best suited for SEO articles, content clusters, keyword planning, content teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. ShortlyAI, meanwhile, shines for blog posts, long form articles, stories, distraction free writing, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Scalenut describes itself as \"AI-powered SEO content lifecycle management platform.\" ShortlyAI, established in 2020, positions itself as \"Distraction-free AI writing tool focused on long-form content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Scalenut** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 5.0), more features (8 vs 2), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean ShortlyAI is a poor choice — far from it. ShortlyAI excels in its own right, particularly for blog posts and long form articles.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value end-to-end seo content workflow in one tool, go with Scalenut. If clean distraction-free interface matters more to you, ShortlyAI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
